<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239611>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Cloeon morna sp. n.: A—male imago; B—male genitalia, ventral view; C—female imago; D—larva." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/239611/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239612>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Cloeon morna sp. n., mouthparts: A—labrum (left ventral view, right dorsal view); B—hypopharynx; C—right mandible; D—left mandible; E—right maxilla; F—labium." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/239612/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239613>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Cloeon morna sp. n., larva: A—gill I; B—gill III; C—gill VII; D—fore leg." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/239613/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239614>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Distal margin of abdominal tergum IV (scale bar 0.05 mm): A— Cloeon morna sp. n.; B— Cloeon sidadi sp. n. Lateral margin of abdominal terga VIII and IX: C— Cloeon morna sp. n.; D— Cloeon sidadi sp. n." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/239614/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239618>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Aquatic habitats in the islands of Santo Antão and Santiago. A—Ribeira da Torre in Xôxô (type locality of Cloeon morna sp. n.); B—pools of Ribeira Tarrafal in Tarrafal de Monte Trigo; C—irrigation system of taro fields common in Santo Antão; D—irrigation cistern in the valley of Ribeira Grande in Cidade Velha (type locality of Cloeon sidadi sp. n.); and E—an unnamed brook in Fontainhas." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/239618/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

